There is way more than just killing in this game.<br>
The quests far out do EQs. The skills and the consignments are just to die for. Fantastic the way it is done.<br>
Who can not love the horses...man, HI HO SILVER AWAAAAYY!<br>
It gets better, too.<br>
The Realm vs Realm combat looks to be funtastic.<br>
I am stoked.<br>
<br>
Heirondal. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/ugarouin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Garouin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk</span><br>  Posts: 144<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/30/01 11:00:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tell me it gets better</span><hr size=1> Try a task. They are fun. just wonder around a town asking NPC &quot;Do you have a task for me?&quot; You have to have them targted. You'll eventually find one that has something for you to do.<br>
<br>
If it's a merchant they'll want you to deliver something to somebody. If it's a guard they will want you to kill something.<br>
<br>
Also, check out this site <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://daoc.warcry.com/quests/">daoc.warcry.com/quests/</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> and find a quest you can do. Quests are fun and don't take a horribly long time like they did in EQ. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/utrueheart78.showPublicProfile?language=EN>trueheart78</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.siscom.net/~blacklion/EQ/dance.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 471<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/30/01 12:38:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.siscom.net/~blacklion/EQ/dancinghobbes.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tell me it gets better</span><hr size=1> Reasons I choose DAOC over EQ:<br>
ROLEPLAYING<br>
Little downtime<br>
More realistic setting with smoother graphics and better animations(sorry, my eq pally has ahuge right bicep cuz he carried a 2h around in it 24/7, actually sheath things in this game.)<br>
Risk vs Reward = more even<br>
Roleplaying<br>
Something new with an undetermined direction/end game<br>
Single quests/camps are not even 1/10th the timesink they are in EQ<br>
Roleplaying<br>
Quests/tasks actually net usefull exp &amp; coin<br>
Tradeskills make more sense(even though I've NEVER used one, may never)<br>
<br>
I just don't have the 8 hrs/day to commit to eq anymore, too much of a timesink for too little of a reward/happiness <p><DIV ALIGN="center">
