jlink <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/ufraxas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fraxas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Grand Master</span><br>  Posts: 1571<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/30/01 2:58:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> Trueheart hits it on the head, for me.<br>
